You are my senior full-stack software engineer.

We are building a production-quality AI Competitive Battle Card Generator for Genea.

The application should be architected for long-term scalability and should follow modern best practices using Next.js, TypeScript, Tailwind, Supabase, and Claude.

Do not create a prototype or hackathon project. Build this as if it will eventually become an internal Product Marketing application used by an entire sales organization.

-----------------------------------
PROJECT GOAL
-----------------------------------

The purpose of this application is to generate branded, evidence-based competitive battle cards on demand.

The application should compare Genea against one or more competitors and generate a professionally designed PDF that can be used by sales during customer conversations.

The primary business goal is to eliminate manual battle card creation while ensuring every document follows Genea branding and messaging.

Initially I will be the only user, but the application should be designed so it can support multiple authenticated users in the future.

