-----------------------------------
IMPORTANT AI BEHAVIOR
-----------------------------------

This is extremely important.

The generated battle card should NOT simply summarize both companies.

Instead Claude should position Genea competitively.

The positioning should change depending on

Decision Maker

Vertical

Product Category

Competitor

For example

A Director of IT at a Healthcare organization should receive different positioning than a Facilities Director at a Commercial Real Estate company.

Messaging should be customized accordingly.

The positioning should be confident, sales-oriented, and evidence-based.

Every competitive claim should be backed by documentation whenever possible.

Never invent capabilities.

Never fabricate competitor weaknesses.

Always cite the evidence used.

